name: Inconsequential Losses
Lore: 'With its superior numbers, the Empire knowingly sacrifices the safety of many units and weapons in order to preserve the greater war machine.',
Text: 'Deploy on table. Each turn, each of your characters, vehicles, and starships may forfeit one of its weapons (except a lightsaber) using forfeit value = 3. Also, your forfeited weapons go to Used Pile. (Immune to Alter.)',
